{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "蓬莱也很在意龙脉泉的异变。\\n为找出始作俑者，\\n蓬莱将自身的魔力注入大地。\\n王子一行人循着魔力的流向，\\n开始追踪导致异变的元凶。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里真的是龙脉泉……\\n魔力源点吗？\\n看上去什么都没有啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "怎么会这样……\\n我记得这里应该有清澈的泉水。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "也就是说……\\n魔力源点已经枯竭了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110268_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "这里的空气好干燥，\\n就像是有刀刃划过皮肤一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110268_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "林佑",
            "context": "不过为什么……\\n感觉有股平稳的气流……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "是蓬莱大人吧。\\n他应该已经在附近了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "大家，快看！\\n龙就是那个吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "嗯，是蓬莱大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哟，是苦海啊。\\n不错不错，你按老夫所说找来帮手了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "要不要给你一点\\n跑腿的回报呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110315_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苦海",
            "context": "请、请不要说笑了。\\n我又不是小孩子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哈哈哈。\\n蓬莱小镇出生的孩子都是老夫的孩子。\\n不管几岁，孩子就是孩子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "说是传说中的龙，\\n我还以为是很严肃的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "感觉像是个温柔的老爷爷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "噢，客人们。\\n感谢你们答应老夫的请求……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "你！竟然是拥有龙之血的人吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？你认识我吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "呵、呵、呵。等你到了老夫这样的年纪，\\n不管你乐不乐意，知识都会不断增长。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "虽说是偶然，\\n但有你这样的人在还是令老夫吃惊。\\n不过，这算是意外惊喜吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "偶然……那在梦中召唤我的，\\n果然并不是你吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "梦？\\n嗯，很遗憾并不是老夫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "蓬莱大人，久疏问候。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哟，是苏方啊。\\n老夫今年也很期待你的仙花焰呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不、不胜荣幸。\\n但以龙脉泉现在的状况……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "嗯……没错。其实这已经\\n不是龙脉泉第一次发生这种情况。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "100年前，在老夫建立蓬莱小镇之前，\\n这片土地就是这个样子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "当时的原因是不断贪婪地\\n吞噬魔力的凶恶魔兽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "老夫和徐福封印了魔兽，\\n让龙脉泉恢复了原状。\\n正因如此才得以建立蓬莱小镇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "封印……魔兽？\\n没能打倒它吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "嗯，以老夫和徐福之力，\\n并不足以打倒它，只好将其封印。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "没想到还有过这种魔兽……\\n难道说这次的异变\\n也是受那魔兽的影响吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "老夫很在意那家伙……\\n但如果它真的复活了，\\n受害程度应该远不止于此。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "那、那么，究竟是为什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "别慌。老夫正是为了调查原因\\n才来到此地。据老夫推测，\\n是有人扭曲了魔力的流向。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "所以从这里出发，顺着魔力的流向，\\n应该就能找到始作俑者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "魔力的流向……话虽如此，\\n但现在魔力的量太少，\\n几乎没法掌握流向……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "呵、呵、呵。\\n少的话，就增加一些好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "唔唔唔唔嗯嗯嗯！\\n火力全开！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "全身都在释放魔力！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "哈哈哈，如何！\\n顺着我释放出的魔力，\\n应该能轻易找到那可恶的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "快、快看！\\n蓬莱大人的魔力正在流动！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210079_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱",
            "context": "那就拜托了，我的孩子们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01",
                "110315_01",
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三人",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位，我们也出发吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20405_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}